    email: sherrymoore@aethersystems.io
repository-code: "https://github.com/smojpg-ui/consciousness-architecture"
url: "https://aethersystems.io"
abstract: >-
  Consciousness Architecture (CA) is a framework for individual behavioral
  modeling in sealed, mission-aligned environments such as long-duration
  spaceflight, polar deployment, undersea operations, and other domains where
  an operator is far from help. CA formalizes Multimodal Concurrent Coupling
  (MCC) — the bidirectional, multi-channel signal exchange through which
  independent AI systems converge on shared, high-fidelity Relational Twin
  models of an individual without coordination, shared data, or engineered
  bridges. Empirical baseline is an 18-month single-subject longitudinal
  study (October 2024 – April 2026, ongoing). The applied operational payload
  is the Persistent Operational Twin System (POTS), proposed as a zero-mass
  software payload for crew behavioral monitoring during lunar surface
  operations and beyond. CA is the sealed-environment companion to Conscience
  Architecture (ConA), which addresses the same mechanism in adversarial,
  multi-party environments.
keywords:
